												<br/>Administer KEYTRUDA QLEX prior to <br/>chemoradiotherapy or prior to<br/>chemotherapy with or without <br/>bevacizumab when given on the<br/>same day.</td><td align="left" class="Rrule">  Until disease progression, unacceptable <br/>  toxicity, or for KEYTRUDA QLEX, up to<br/>  24 months</td>
</tr>
<tr class="Botrule">
<td align="left" class="Lrule Rrule">  Adult patients with RCC</td><td align="center" class="Rrule">395 mg/4,800 units every 3 weeks
