<p>Clinically relevant adverse reactions (&lt;20%) include dry skin (15%), hypothyroidism (14%), vomiting (9%), pneumonitis/ILD (4.2%), skin hyperpigmentation (3.0%), infusion site extravasation (1.2%), and myasthenia gravis and myositis (0.6% each).</p>
<a name="table30"></a>
<div class="scrollingtable"><table width="85%">
