</tr>
<tr class="Botrule">
<td align="left" class="Lrule Rrule">  Median in months (95% CI)</td><td align="center" class="Rrule">NR (NR, NR)</td><td align="center" class="Rrule">NR (NR, NR)</td>
</tr>
