</table></div>
<p>For patients with PD-L1 positive tumors, the RFS HR was 0.54 (95% CI: 0.42, 0.69); p&lt;0.0001. For patients with PD-L1 positive tumors, the DMFS HR was 0.61 (95% CI: 0.49, 0.76); p&lt;0.0001. The RFS and DMFS benefit for intravenous pembrolizumab compared to placebo was observed regardless of tumor PD-L1 expression.</p>
