</tr>
</tbody>
</table></div>
<p>At the protocol-specified final OS analysis, the median in the intravenous pembrolizumab in combination with pemetrexed and platinum chemotherapy arm was 22.0 months (95% CI: 19.5, 24.5) compared to 10.6 months (95% CI: 8.7, 13.6) in the placebo with pemetrexed and platinum chemotherapy arm, with an HR of 0.56 (95% CI: 0.46, 0.69).</p>
